pg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tulum-luxury-apartment-interior-living-room-220525-1255-03-1365x2048.jpg 1365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1706px) 100vw, 1706px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1706\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tulum-luxury-apartment-interior-living-room-220525-1255-04.jpg\" alt=\"A serene, terracotta-toned living space showcases earthy textures, warm natural light, and a refined material palette. Walls in sunbaked hues form a calming backdrop for relaxed sofas, woven rugs, and solid wood furniture with primitive silhouettes. \" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tulum-luxury-apartment-interior-living-room-220525-1255-04.jpg 1706w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tulum-luxury-apartment-interior-living-room-220525-1255-04-940x1411.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tulum-luxury-apartment-interior-living-room-220525-1255-04-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tulum-luxury-apartment-interior-living-room-220525-1255-04-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tulum-luxury-apartment-interior-living-room-220525-1255-04-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tulum-luxury-apartment-interior-living-room-220525-1255-04-1365x2048.jpg 1365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1706px) 100vw, 1706px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn another apartment, neutral tones and organic materials take center stage in the living room. Filtered sunlight washes over a minimalist sofa, sculptural wood tables, and a layered jute rug, creating a space that feels both serene and elemental.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1706\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.